  </section>

  <!-- About Title -->
  <section class="about-info">
    <section class="about-title">
      <h1>ABOUT US</h1>
    </section>
    <!-- About Data -->
    <div class="about-head">
      <p>"Empowering learners to achieve their dreams, one course at a time.</p>
      <p> At Scholar's Lore, we believe that education is the key to unlocking potential and transforming lives."</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-data">
      <p>
        At <strong>Scholar's Lore</strong>, we believe in the transformative power of education. Founded with the
        mission to make learning accessible to everyone, we have grown into a platform trusted by millions of learners
        worldwide. Our goal is simple: to empower individuals with the knowledge and skills they need to thrive in
        their personal and professional lives.
      </p>

      <table class="about-table">
        <tr>
          <th colspan="2">Our Mission</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td colspan="2">
            We aim to bridge the gap between ambition and achievement by providing high-quality, affordable education.
            Whether you're looking to upskill, switch careers, or dive into a new hobby, Scholar's Lore offers a diverse
            range of courses designed to meet your unique needs.
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <table class="about-table">
        <tr>
          <th colspan="2">What We Offer</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="icon-cell"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i></td>
          <td class="content-cell"><strong>Expert-Led Courses:</strong> Learn from top industry professionals and thought leaders.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="icon-cell"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i></td>
          <td class="content-cell"><strong>Interactive Learning:</strong> Engage with hands-on projects, quizzes, and live sessions to enhance your understanding.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="icon-cell"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i></td>
          <td class="content-cell"><strong>Flexible Access:</strong> Study at your own pace, anytime, anywhere, with lifetime access to course materials.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="icon-cell"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i></td>
          <td class="content-cell"><strong>Recognized Certifications:</strong> Boost your resume and career prospects with certifications that validate your skills.</td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <table class="about-table">
        <tr>
          <th colspan="2">Our Vision</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td colspan="2">
            We envision a world where education is not bound by borders, where learners from every corner of the globe can
            access quality learning resources. By partnering with leading organizations and experts, we strive to create a
            community that fosters growth, innovation, and lifelong learning.
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <table class="about-table">
        <tr>
          <th colspan="2">Our Values</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="icon-cell"><i class="fas fa-heart"></i></td>
          <td class="content-cell"><strong>Inclusivity:</strong> Education for everyone, everywhere.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="icon-cell"><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i></td>
          <td class="content-cell"><strong>Innovation:</strong> Continuously evolving to meet the changing needs of learners.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="icon-cell"><i class="fas fa-award"></i></td>
          <td class="content-cell"><strong>Excellence:</strong> Delivering top-notch content and user experience.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="icon-cell"><i class="fas fa-users"></i></td>
          <td class="content-cell"><strong>Community:</strong> Building a global network of learners and educators.</td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <table class="about-table">
        <tr>
          <th colspan="3">Contributors</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <div class="contributor-box">
              <img src="public/img/HirdepalSingh.jpeg" alt="Contributor1">
              <p>Hirdepal Singh</p>
            </div>
          </td>
          <td>
            <div class="contributor-box">
              <img src="public/img/JaijitSingh.jpg" alt="Contributor2">
              <p>Jaijit Singh</p>
            </div>
          </td>
          <td>
            <div class="contributor-box">
              <img src="public/img/JaskiratSingh.jpg" alt="Contributor3">
              <p>Jaskirat Singh</p>
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <table class="about-table">
        <tr>
          <th colspan="2">Join Us on Our Journey</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td colspan="2">
            At Scholar's Lore, every learner's success is our success. Together, we can unlock your potential and
            achieve greatness. Join our growing community today and take the first step toward a brighter future.
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<style>
.about-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  margin: 2rem 0;
  background: white;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  border-radius: 10px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.about-table th {
  background: #1e212e;
  color: white;
  padding: 1rem;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.about-table td {
  padding: 1rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  vertical-align: top;
}

.about-table tr:last-child td {
  border-bottom: none;
}

.about-table i {
  color: #f9c87b;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.icon-cell {
  width: 50px;
  text-align: left;
  padding-right: 0;
}

.content-cell {
  padding-left: 0.5rem;
  text-align: left;
}

.contributor-box {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 1rem;
}

.contributor-box img {
  width: 100px;
  height: 120px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  object-fit: cover;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.contributor-box p {
  margin: 0;
  font-weight: 500;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .about-table {
    display: block;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  
  .contributor-box img {
    width: 80px;
    height: 100px;
  }

  .icon-cell {
    width: 40px;
  }
}
</style>

